#NEWS: The weather in Dubai is IDEAL park weather right now, there's a nice breeze and rain is refusing to fall (for the most part!). Which is why food festivals and outdoor foodie markets are cropping up all over the city - the demand is huge!

But if you're going to visit just one food festival this year, this is the one you need to hit:

Eat The World DXB is happening this weekend at Burj Park and, as always, they're pulling out all the stops to make sure it remains the cities best. Read the full article and get all the deets on the site! @eattheworlddxb @dubaifoodfest #food #foodies #news #announcements #lovindubai
